safest possible route
low-risk navigation paths
🔐 Security & Privacy Layer
End-to-end encryption
Minimal data collection
On-device processing priority
User-controlled permissions
⚡ Key Design Principles
1. Low Latency First

Critical decisions happen on-device (< 1 second response time)

2. Privacy by Design

Audio is processed locally, not streamed to cloud

3. Hybrid Architecture
Device = detection + reaction
Cloud = coordination + storage
4. Fail-Safe Operation
Works with weak or no internet
SMS fallback for emergencies
